en_US: Convert parts into terrain with ease.
Check for updates on Studio launch and display a notice when the plugin is outdated.
Deletes the part after being converted to Terrain.
Highlight the part when the mouse is hovers over the part.
Parts with their Locked property set to true will not be converted.

Existing terrain will not be overwritten.

NOTE: Air will delete terrain regardless of setting.
Ignoring locked part due to settings.
